{"tid":2429023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"知名寶寶米餅「噁心工廠」直擊！蟑螂老鼠滿地爬　工業氮氣包裝","createTime":"2021-03-02T04:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:59:26.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1501120042363ea3273747b6c15ccb37272c86da","tid":2429023,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/49nPmDR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F49nPmDR.png&h=dcb580bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NgGjOAt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNgGjOAt.png&h=66fadd21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QcoLKi4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQcoLKi4.png&h=ff2e9593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2dBUZXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2dBUZXc.png&h=8f01ddf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/urjCBcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FurjCBcn.png&h=e4f1d083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XlsEAow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXlsEAow.png&h=c77d0d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7HhWnGw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7HhWnGw.png&h=629c5bf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2月26日下午，新北市衛生局稽查人員會同新北市調查處調查官，突襲位於新北市中和區<br />\n中正工業大樓7樓的樂扉寶寶米餅廠房，查緝人員一進到廠房便大聲喝斥：「不要動！」<br />\n現場工作人員對於大批稽查人員突如其來的搜索行動，都感到相當錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員控制現場後前往產線檢查，果然發現瓶身上標註「禁用於食品」的工業用氮氣鋼<br />\n瓶，正以管線連接到包裝機台上，對嬰幼兒食用的米餅進行充氣包裝，旋即要求員工關閉<br />\n機台，並當場查扣所有工業用氮氣鋼瓶。<br />\n <br />\n寶寶米餅爆食安危機！知名嬰幼兒食品廠商樂扉遭前員工檢舉，指公司為節省成本，竟違<br />\n法以工業用氮氣填充寶寶米餅包裝，調查局及衛生單位日前搜索該公司，當場封存有疑慮<br />\n的產品並勒令限期改善。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210302/1928842.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210302%2F1928842.htm&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=00e6998c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210302/1928842.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3bcf5a3dd375c216fcbfb32d20c64c56e970318b","tid":2429023,"uid":204539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"台灣啲預先包裝食品有啲都好伏吓<br />\n似係食緊另一set元素周期表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e0765001642415a7f83b2356d360c7e8d32b4d","tid":2429023,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"啲台商好多去咗大陸取經 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897c9f3598e9b1a1785b03680984305a45d256ca","tid":2429023,"uid":301820,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:30:05.000Z","msg":"本來臺灣國食品安全<br />\n不嬲唔多好，但有改進<br />\n<br />\n馬共九上台後<br />\n又搞到臺灣七國咁亂<br />\n奶共貪腐一直鋪路<br />\n急進融合令資金流失<br />\n<br />\n而家成班奶共奸商<br />\n將支那果套帶番臺灣國<br />\n小英真係有排執，下屆都可能搞唔掂"},{"pid":"5f61c96c46c68575bc3736e5aa5bbcef1d9f428a","tid":2429023,"uid":301820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"897c9f3598e9b1a1785b03680984305a45d256ca","tid":2429023,"uid":301820,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:30:05.000Z","msg":"本來臺灣國食品安全<br />\n不嬲唔多好，但有改進<br />\n<br />\n馬共九上台後<br />\n又搞到臺灣七國咁亂<br />\n奶共貪腐一直鋪路<br />\n急進融合令資金流失<br />\n<br />\n而家成班奶共奸商<br />\n將支那果套帶番臺灣國<br />\n小英真係有排執，下屆都可能搞唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13023b16b6693c9d113fe506918dfd1def47a88f","tid":2429023,"uid":222238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"台灣藍屍"},{"pid":"e986421c48071d537eeb55d8f540c4b12a256c51","tid":2429023,"uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:59:26.000